description: Type of action performed by the Wooclap user identified by participant_id
Unique ID of the Wooclap event that includes the question identified by object_id
Unique ID of a Wooclap participant.
Timestamp of the action, the timezone is UTC. Its format varies according to the database, but the information always includes year, month, day, hour, minutes, seconds
When type = ‘question-answer’, it is the unique ID of the question that got an answer. The question belongs to the event identified by event_id.
